Title: Whose Vault Is It Anyway?
Description:
I do not know what we will find in the vault or why Sarkareth wants access to it, but I hope we are not too late.

Before we continue any further, Tuberros should lead Rannan and Perisimona back to Loamm.

Come and talk to me once you are ready to move forward.
ObjectivesText: Talk to Emberthal once you are ready to go.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Emberthal outside of Nal ks'kol
